6 A BILL
7 TO BE ENTITLED
8 AN ACT
9
10 Relating to the Public Service Commission; to establish
11 the Power to the People Act; to amend Sections 37-1-1, 37-1-3,
12 37-1-5, and 37-1-12, Code of Alabama 1975; to revise the
13 membership and terms of the public service commissioners; to
14 establish the Secretary of Energy as a cabinet member
15 appointed by the Governor and provide for the duties of the
16 secretary; to add Sections 37-1-81.1 and 37-1-81.2 to the Code
17 of Alabama 1975, to prohibit an increase in electric retail
18 base rates for a certain period and thereafter prohibit
19 electric utilities from including certain costs in the
20 calculation or determination of rates or service regulations;
21 to require the commission to hold a public meeting at least
22 annually; to amend Sections 17-14-2, 17-14-3, and 36-3-1, Code
23 of Alabama 1975, to make conforming changes; to repeal Section
24 37-1-9, Code of Alabama 1975, relating to public service
25 commissioners; and to make nonsubstantive, technical revisions
26 to update the existing code language to current style.
27 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
