266 "§36-3-1
267 The Governor, Lieutenant Governor, Attorney General,
268 Auditor, Secretary of State, Treasurer, and Commissioner of
269 Agriculture and Industries, the President of the Public
270 Service Commission and two associate public service
271 commissioners shall hold their respective offices for the term
272 of four years from the time of their installation in office
273 and until their successors shall be elected and qualified,
274 such installation to take place on the first Monday after the
275 second Tuesday in January next after their election."
276 Section 5. Section 37-1-9, Code of Alabama 1975,
